high_descs: Go across the room, turn right to face the toaster.
Pick up the knife in front of the toaster.
Turn around and head to the fridge.
Cut the apple on the top shelf of the fridge.
Turn left, go across the room and head to the cabinet above the microwave.
Open the second cabinet above the counter and put the knife in the cabinet.
Turn around and head back to the fridge.
Pick up a slice of apple from the fridge.
Turn left and head to the sink.
Put the apple in the bowl in the sink.
Pick up the bowl from the sink.
Turn around and head back to the fridge.
Put the bowl on the top shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put an apple in a bowl in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk forward and turn right to face the white table.
Pick up the knife on the white table.
Turn around and step forward to face the top of the fridge.
Cut the apple in the top of the fridge into three slices.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the cabinet above the right side of the microwave.
Place the knife in the cabinet above the right side of the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the fridge on the left.
Take a piece of apple out of the top of the fridge.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the sink.
Place the apple in the bowl in the sink.
Pick up the bowl with a piece of apple in it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the fridge on the left.
Place the bowl with an apple piece in it in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To put a piece of apple in a bowl plus place them in the fridge.

high_descs: Walk forward seven steps then turn right and go to the white table.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle from the table.
Turn left until hitting the wall, then left again straight to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, cut the apple into three pieces then close it.
Turn left, go forward until the end of the table, then right until hitting the wall, then go right to spot between the microwave and sink before looking at the cabinets above it.
Open the cabinet, put the knife inside and close it.
Turn around and walk forward until the wall then turn left to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, pick up the apple slice on the right then close it.
Turn around walk forward until the stove then turn right and go to the sink.
Put the apple slice in the bowl in the sink.
Pick up the bowl with the apple slice in it.
Turn around, go straight to the wall then turn left to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and put the bowl in the upper shelf of the lower section of it.
anns.task_desc: Put the knife in the cabinet and the apple slice in a bowl in the refrigerator.
